  "content_html": "<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-d6d71401-9581-4259-8f80-9ed1420d6874\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-83ef5b0f-ac2c-4224-b0e3-768957c55d11\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs15 se-ff-nanumgothic se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-43ae32e4-e967-4858-830a-30d9f9b90272\" style=\"color:#0095e9;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>Story Boarding DAY 26</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-b27cf33b-a368-44f8-9d7f-dee4ee90453f\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs15 se-ff-nanumgothic se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-43eb1831-b2fc-48c2-8c7d-7c61285ce715\" style=\"color:#0095e9;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>​</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-1b739bf5-c94e-47b2-a86c-2ae3565334c5\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs15 se-ff-nanumgothic se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-300d154f-b48f-4675-936b-3e92f8bf2d4d\" style=\"color:#ff5f45;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>[본격적인 스토리보딩 작업]</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-1a84d2c0-e7a0-4be5-bf18-6fb5b67d9403\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs15 se-ff-nanumgothic se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-b20a6adb-d73c-40eb-9af6-0ef47119cd7a\" style=\"color:#ff5f45;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>이제 본격적으로 스토리보딩 작업에 들어갑니다. 지금까지는 자료나 개념에 대해 심도있게 생각했습니다. 물론 아직은 미흡한 부분이나 보강해야하는 사항이 있지만 앞으로 채워나가도록 하겠습니다. 이제부터는 하나하나 PPT 파일을 정리하도록 하겠습니다. 이제 시작입니다. 약 두달 뒤 나름 완벽한 (주)파파스컴퍼니 기획문서가 완성되기를 희망해 봅니다.</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-bffd70f2-6757-469d-a444-44cb0911bc43\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs15 se-ff-nanumgothic se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-839adbf2-0293-4ef2-a655-92da68b0d682\" style=\"color:#ff5f45;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>​</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-4b2d25c5-d02c-4d72-9a4f-8bc729c59bd3\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs15 se-ff-nanumgothic se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-916754cb-b5df-4769-8c53-5a54fe24a497\" style=\"color:#ff5f45;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>\"</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-98797ac2-5343-475b-b52d-cd2a06f27a2c\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs15 se-ff-nanumgothic se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-02d2e6eb-a324-4263-a504-ef7159ba8cb3\" style=\"color:#ff5f45;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>형식이 실질을 잡아먹는다. 가장 형식적인 문서를 만들도록 노력하겠습니다.</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-0b0e995a-2079-4a5b-baf7-02252b098cf6\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs15 se-ff-nanumgothic se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-bad60eaf-376b-46ed-b753-97edf454dc5f\" style=\"color:#ff5f45;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>\"</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-4da37906-334c-4bc0-bb7f-b29093c9d7e9\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs15 se-ff-nanumgothic se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-34b29408-ae4e-49d1-b855-d77ee9077aa7\" style=\"color:#ff5f45;\"><b>​</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> \n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-30502fd0-6a5f-41fc-b375-022b84c65bfe\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-cb82f05c-a662-4358-b28f-b81924462501\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff- se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-8069e34b-5e6e-463f-b1ec-4224b9467361\" style=\"color:#000000;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>Tip1. 위치, 배치에 따른 UI</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-2eb55faf-8a48-4d30-81f7-6fbe3f03ab7e\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff- se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-f656faf9-6e06-4be2-818f-c8f415f6959f\" style=\"color:#000000;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>Tip2. 클릭, 이벤트와 연동</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-83d6b4e6-f7cf-4c38-8f83-bea03e6fdfc9\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff- se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-cf2dfbd0-8d7b-43df-bfc1-4815e00892be\" style=\"color:#ff0010;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>Tip3. 중복과 모양</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-7c16f69a-9b28-4cfa-8aa0-4ea2084a6ec4\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff- se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-7dd4c00c-e1f1-418b-b317-22447f9c2688\" style=\"color:#000000;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>Tip4. 프로세스에 맞는 구성</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-de532f42-2335-4a48-b33d-0f0a2de0b52e\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff- se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-4005b169-d8fc-40c1-8aa8-d144008bacae\" style=\"color:#000000;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>Tip5. 정확한 전달</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-88b11e3d-99e0-4276-a687-7c5dc2b7d17b\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff- se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-364cb525-b673-40b2-8010-e95f667ff93f\" style=\"color:#000000;\"><b>​</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-e3d94fa3-5633-43ba-9916-ad19f58b3352\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-5029dd51-2e31-46b2-9509-6d67450b9f9c\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">모바일 UI 구성시 주의사항을 계속해서 올립니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-default\" id=\"SE-af07c4c0-f46c-4d5d-9e05-7594eec2dae8\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n<hr class=\"se-hr\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-6a9492b9-a841-45f6-946f-76998a3d1c8a\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-2eeb7aa1-5771-461c-8742-2d47f306d61d\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff- se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-9aaadd4c-e604-41f2-9c37-482508897aa6\" style=\"color:#000000;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>Tip3. 중복과 모양</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-9aec8381-e482-4b98-92bc-d3f5ff577d0d\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/222906655306/001.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-327cb3ad-93f3-42e2-bfcd-673a4bb12500\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-27ae62b2-2bcb-44e3-8353-52166d35d33f\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff- se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-58205543-4d92-4d40-a314-e9b2dd3ed1c3\" style=\"color:#000000;background-color:#ffffff;\"><a class=\"se-link\" href=\"https://www.smashingmagazine.com/2009/03/breadcrumbs-in-web-design-examples-and-best-practices/\" target=\"_blank\"><b>https://www.smashingmagazine.com/2009/03/breadcrumbs-in-web-design-examples-and-best-practices/</b></a></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-8f005b81-fb74-4bad-86ba-f437939c7cbb\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/222906655306/002.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-line2\" id=\"SE-2d590927-2b20-4036-a016-c5d16c51f7f9\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-line2 se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n<hr class=\"se-hr\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-0f3cd5b9-e02d-46fa-84f5-6e9cbdfbbce2\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-ce367c22-70e0-4869-9389-5916735eb7f8\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff- se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-4c24101a-e630-436c-b3dd-1206aa085b86\" style=\"color:#000000;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>스플래시 스토리보드</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-aad4841e-920b-469c-b6a3-dd9d8fc8ab60\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-fa9b2520-b1c5-4be1-88c2-2ec9030d34a3\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">스플래시란 다음과 같은 역할을 하는 첫화면 성격의 이미지 스토리텔링입니다. 메인화면에 입장하기 전에 이 앱이 전달하는 기능이나 취지를 임팩트있게 만드는데 의미가 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-9cb43373-1ce1-4bb7-adf9-68f496fae003\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-8d064247-77eb-4d73-abfa-4bd91cbf9314\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-line5\" id=\"SE-b901793d-48f3-43bc-a0ac-89b254777fcc\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-line5 se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n<hr class=\"se-hr\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-ee176251-da99-4867-a75f-396685e9abaf\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-9a803965-5151-4256-8bd1-d5b13c2beb89\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-b781f4ed-7142-465e-b5bc-e36dc57b6a72\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>모바일앱의 시작, 스플래시 화면</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-8be30761-742b-43d9-8216-5e242590586c\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-d149e817-02c3-427b-9cfb-a39744a98d92\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">모바일 앱(Mobile App) 실행시에 가장 처음 노출되도록 실행되는 작업으로 짧게는 1초에서 길게는 5초까지(평균 3초가 적당합니다.) 이어지는 앱과 사용자의 처음 연결고리역할을 하는 파트입니다. 가장 짧은 시간동안 로고나 대표이미지 또는 임팩트 있는 슬로건으로 시선을 사로잡는 역할을 하지만 기본적으로는 시각적인 즐거움보다는 앱의 첫시작과 재방문에 따른 타입을 다르게 설정하여 사용자가 살아있는 앱이라고 판단하도록 하는 목적으로 사용되기도 합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-4412434b-de40-48f2-9a44-c067468ac198\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-2ee0d1bb-c731-4682-8c07-c9fbd409a126\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-03333a33-4977-49d8-b9b4-d2a02e9355a8\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-2eab1f24-1817-4b54-bc3b-35699a41b592\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>스플래시의 목적</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-73081e13-e763-4e7a-89c0-c998321f73d4\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-b347feec-da74-4f04-8743-cdf17baf680c\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">가장 중요한것은 기대감입니다. 이 앱에 대한 첫인상을 긴장감있게 준비하게 만드는데 목적이 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-9effa4c3-642a-4320-894c-8bd35f3ff056\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-8ce0d3aa-4452-486b-9d31-a59a0ba838f6\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">두번째는 앱에 대한 원페이지 서비스 요약입니다.  스플래시를 통해 이 앱의 원페이지 특징을 읽을 수 있으면 베스트입니다. 만약 로고가 인지도가 있다면 로그만 부각시키는 것도 하나의 방법입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-b4fe8b81-5c36-49c2-b91a-1dce1b10c215\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-e079f5c9-81f8-485c-babe-100785876c35\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-0155c5c9-fe5f-47dd-95b3-e472a634351a\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-1d26d0df-488e-4d6a-aacf-c9dfbf920015\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-5969c12b-a727-4619-a4be-d5047d07bd84\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-a7f4f7f6-69e3-4a46-92ca-5bedbd69e664\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-6e057f2e-2d5b-4df3-bce4-f346aa8ecd5b\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-f419ccee-0038-4723-bbf9-b6c8fe69abf6\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">다음 동영상 예시를 보면서 시작하겠습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-2348a1b5-38a7-4d2e-b3cf-5364502a417f\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-b9f6efac-8176-4b7b-9bcf-4e885b37415d\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-video se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-video se-section-align- se-l-default\" style=\"max-width:334px;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-video\" id=\"SE-db617bb0-92c6-45da-9fe3-fb7f5894dcb6\">\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-9500f24c-d955-401f-96bb-716a8ffa0b99\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-s